title: PLANT BASED CHOCOLATE SHAKE
subtitle: MADE WITH FRESH CREAM
ingredients: Water, coconut milk, sugar, maltodextrin, low fat cocoa powder (1.9%), stabilisers (carboxymethylcellulose, cellulose), vanilla extract, salt. May contain traces of allergens: milk and gluten.

title: BELGIAN CHOCOLATE CUSTARD
subtitle: WITH FAIRLY TRADED BEANS
ingredients: Water, skimmed milk powder, sugar, modified starch, Belgian chocolate (2.5%) [sugar, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, emulsifier (soya lecithin), natural flavouring], double cream (milk), fat reduced cocoa powder.

title: CHOCOLATE MILKSHAKE
subtitle: CHOCOLATE MILKSHAKE
ingredients: Whole milk (67%) Semi skimmed milk, water, sugar, fat reduced cocoa powder (1.6%), Belgian chocolate powder (sugar, cocoa mass, fat reduced cocoa powder, natural vanilla flavouring), stabilisers (carboxymethylcellulose), salt. For allergens see ingredients in bold. Always check your packaging for the most up to date information.

title: MADAGASCAN VANILLA CUSTARD
subtitle: WITH BOURBON VANILLA
ingredients: Water, skimmed milk powder, sugar, double cream (milk), modified starch, Madagascan bourbon vanilla extract, cream powder (milk), colour (beta-carotene).

title: STRAWBERRY COULIS
subtitle: WITH ENGLISH SEA SALT
ingredients: invert sugar syrup, strawberries (36%), water, cornflour, concentrated lemon juice, acidity regulator (citric acid), preservative (potassium sorbate).

title: FLAT WHITE COFFEE
subtitle: WITH ENGLISH SEA SALT
ingredients: Semi skimmed milk (82%), coffee (13.6%) (water, arabica coffee extract), sugar, stabilisers (carboxymethylcellulose, cellulose), acidity regulator (sodium bicarbonate). For allergens see ingredients in bold. Always check your packaging for the most up to date information.
